events.title: February 2026 CINLUG Meeting -- Command-Line Tools Micro-Talks
events.description:
CINLUG | Central Indiana Linux Users Group
Last month, Mike Slattery introduced us to a new generation of command-line tools. However, there are so many of the \`old\` tools that we decided for February that we would have a series of micro-talks about some of our attendees' favorite or little-known-about ones!

So come to our Wednesday, February 4th meeting to hear abut them. The meeting starts at 18:30 (6:30 PM) EST.

But don't just come to listen... come **and participate**! We're still lookin
